929
01:07:18,101 --> 01:07:20,304
Yeah. And I've got medicine in my bag.

930
01:07:20,404 --> 01:07:23,637
I could use a nice stiff drink though,
if you'd be so kind.

931
01:07:26,841 --> 01:07:29,246
- It's in my legs.
- I have an old friend who's a doctor.

932
01:07:29,346 --> 01:07:33,110
- His house is on the way.
- No, no, no. I'll be fine, really.

933
01:07:33,750 --> 01:07:35,683
We need to take him to the doctor's.

934
01:07:44,259 --> 01:07:47,831
- Hello.
- <i>Hey, doc. It's George. Are you busy?</i>

935
01:07:47,931 --> 01:07:50,400
<i>I have someone with me
who needs looking at.</i>

936
01:07:50,500 --> 01:07:52,235
- Is it urgent?
- <i>I don't know. It might be.</i>

937
01:07:52,335 --> 01:07:55,771
<i>And get this, it's Errol Flynn.</i>

938
01:07:56,940 --> 01:08:00,474
Okay. Bring him straight away.

939
01:08:01,744 --> 01:08:04,078
