940
01:08:13,956 --> 01:08:16,593
- Great to meet you, Errol.
- Pleasure, doctor.

941
01:08:16,693 --> 01:08:20,063
And this is Beverly Aadland,
my small companion.

942
01:08:20,163 --> 01:08:22,766
I told Cynthia
not to call anyone, but...

943
01:08:22,866 --> 01:08:25,344
Shall we go into the den
so I can take a look at you?

944
01:08:25,444 --> 01:08:27,901
Later, later, old sport.

945
01:08:30,339 --> 01:08:32,306
Hello, everyone.

946
01:08:33,809 --> 01:08:37,481
You all remember who John Barrymore was?

947
01:08:37,881 --> 01:08:40,484
One of the greatest actors
of his generation, right?

948
01:08:40,584 --> 01:08:42,052
- Of course.
- Yeah.

949
01:08:42,152 --> 01:08:45,638
Well, he just died.

950
01:08:46,822 --> 01:08:50,961
Been a tremendous friend of mine,
and of the director, Raoul Walsh's.

951
01:08:51,061 --> 01:08:54,798
And well, while I was out
drowning my sorrow in vodka,

952
01:08:54,898 --> 01:08:58,802
Raoul hightailed it over
to the mortuary.

953
01:08:58,902 --> 01:09:00,670
And he's told the mortician that

954
