01:13:01,411 --> 01:13:03,013
<i>What's the news this week, Hedda?</i>

1007
01:13:03,113 --> 01:13:06,975
<i>Well, I for one, am fed to the teeth
with all the drool</i>

1008
01:13:07,075 --> 01:13:11,555
<i>about Errol Flynn and the Aadland ladies.
