1009
01:13:11,655 --> 01:13:15,225
<i>We've known for years
what a roué Flynn was.</i>

1010
01:13:15,325 --> 01:13:20,627
<i>And he met his match in Beverly,
a teen hellcat...</i>

1011
01:13:28,270 --> 01:13:32,342
<i>As for the peg-legged scheming mother,
well, Mrs. Aadland,</i>

1012
01:13:32,442 --> 01:13:35,178
<i>in this state there is
